## Import

**Project-scoped binding** — `<project>/<user>/<role>`:

```shell
terraform import akka_role_binding.dev_alice my-project/alice@example.com/developer
```

**Organization-scoped binding** — `organization/<user>/<role>`:

```shell
terraform import akka_role_binding.org_admin organization/bob@example.com/admin
```
